    public interface FluentControl
extends SearchControl<FluentWebElement>, AwaitControl, InputControl, JavascriptControl, AlertControl, SnapshotControl, EventsControl, NavigationControl, SeleniumDriverControl, CssControl, FluentInjectControl, ComponentInstantiator, CapabilitiesControl, Configuration
    Global control interface for FluentLenium.

    It allow to control with a Fluent interface the underlying WebDriver.
